	   <tr><td colspan=2>   It really is a personal preference. The three best stats to look for are Agility, Dexterity, and Strength, I prefer to choose one and pour as much as I can into it, then take the few extra and disperse them however. <br>   If you have strength you hit hard, if you have agility you live longer, if you have dexterity you are that much richer.<br><br>   Short rogues RULE!!!<br><br>&nbsp;<br>§Dark Sorrow§</td></tr>
